{"tid":1302952,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"絲打們，你地係有能力搞到D狗身敗名裂","createTime":"2019-07-10T06:33:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T11:07:21.000Z","uid":70786,"like":102,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"71584bd27b2cd894f5734f3d076e3ceb5dbb973b","tid":1302952,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T06:33:31.000Z","msg":"大家有發夢都知D絲打幾高質，人靚心善聲甜<br />\n反觀狗隊入面D狗乸隻隻都男人婆咁<br />\n咁D狗都有生理需要架嘛<br />\n所以佢地通常都會出去搵食<br />\n黃絲們就好易成為目標<br />\n<br />\n提供一兩個sample俾你地參考下<br />\n<br />\n警察真係好受啲囡歡迎 讚賞非抹黑（偷食系列）<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1302844\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1302844</a><br />\n<br />\n!!!!多圖有真相, 深水埗白衫黑警濫權約人入警署扑野!!!!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1302846\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1302846</a><br />\n<br />\n絲打們<br />\n做幾多自己衡量<br />\n記住D狗係點對你地兄弟姊妹<br />\n你地就忍辱負重撚翻D狗<br />\n要佢地落咗更媾女都冇得放鬆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最緊要係保護自己<br />\n不過絲打們個個都係醒目女<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我就唔擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db8ef90a12ee0f0e1f79a43600a7424b11b18364","tid":1302952,"uid":70786,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T06:35:08.000Z","msg":"巴打們撚狗公都有一手<br />\n大家仲記唔記得D巴打扮絲打約戰POST<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7d2c72981d9e54ed3abb104e7835b91d06a567b","tid":1302952,"uid":156326,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T06:35:09.000Z","msg":"你會唔落場搵Madam先"},{"pid":"acabb63f0208ef20c5bc28a2ff750649814aaa46","tid":1302952,"uid":63610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T06:35:15.000Z","msg":"絲打加油！"},{"pid":"6ef4f5b7b5b2354e0e198639f4f3c064865a4a2c","tid":1302952,"uid":70786,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T06:37:35.000Z","msg":"如果都係怕D狗<br />\n可以影D冇樣同難以識別身份嘅軍糧相<br />\n交俾手足們<br 